org.snakeskin.runtime

Class SnakeskinRuntime

  • org.snakeskin.runtime.SnakeskinRuntime

  • public class SnakeskinRuntime

    SnakeSkin runtime object. This object can be used to access various information about the running instance of SnakeSkin
